ack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6bx","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":33999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/02\/16\/hasan-ilm-two-types\/","url_meta":{"origin":23779,"position":0},"title":"Hasan on \u2018Ilm: Knowledge is two types, beneficial or hypocritical","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cKnowledge is two types: Knowledge in the heart is that which benefits. Knowledge on the tongue will be an indictment against the son of Adam.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 376 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0647\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25386,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/05\/ali-silence-ilm\/","url_meta":{"origin":23779,"position":1},"title":"Ali on &#8216;Ilm: No good in silence on beneficial knowledge","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Razi reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThere is no good in silence when it comes to knowledge, just as there is no good in speaking when it comes to ignorance.\u201d Source: al-Tafsi\u0304r al-Kabi\u0304r 2:30 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0627\u0632\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22218,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/03\/13\/ibn-abbas-narrate-understand\/","url_meta":{"origin":23779,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Teaching: Narrate only what people can understand","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 13, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cNarrate to people only what they can understand. Do you want them to deny Allah and his messenger?\u201d Abu Hisham said, \u201cI never narrated anything people did not understand but that it led them astray.\u201d Source: Ja\u0304mi\u2019\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22778,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/04\/28\/ibn-masud-knowledge-fear-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23779,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on &#8216;Ilm: True knowledge is in the fear of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah reported: Ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cKnowledge is not knowing many narrations. Verily, knowledge is the fear of Allah.\u201d Source: Rawd\u0323at al-\u2018Uqala\u0304 9 Ibn Rajab said, \u201cKnowledge is not memorizing many narrations or sayings, but rather it is a light that Allah places in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33402,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/09\/ibn-abbas-knowledge-lost\/","url_meta":{"origin":23779,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Death: This is how Islamic knowledge is lost","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Zuhri reported: When they lowered Zayd ibn Thabit, may Allah be pleased with him, into his grave, Ibn Abbas said, \u201cWhoever would like to see how knowledge is lost, this here is the loss of knowledge.\u201d Source: Ta\u0304ri\u0304kh Dimashq 18053 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u0651\u064f\u0647\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0644\u064e\u0645\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u062f\u064f\u0644\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0632\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u062b\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u062a\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5697,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/30\/talab-ilm-wajib-faridah\/","url_meta":{"origin":23779,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Learning: Seeking knowledge an obligation on every Muslim","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 30, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeeking knowledge is an obligation upon every Muslim.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 22